title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & Similar Matl.
description: Imports Intra Eu - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & Similar Matl. in the United Kingdom decreased to 100.72 GBP Million in September from 104.88 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mica & in the United Kingdom averaged 49.53 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 113.90 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 16.22 GBP Million in August of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Stone, Plaster, Cement, Mic.
